1-(5-tert-butyl-1,2-oxazol-3-yl)-3-(3-hydroxyphenyl)urea and 4-chloro-7-methoxy-5-(oxan-4-yloxy)quinazoline react together in the presence of propan-2-ol, carbonate, cesium(1+) to produce 1-(5-tert-butyl-1,2-oxazol-3-yl)-3-[3-[7-methoxy-5-(oxan-4-yloxy)quinazolin-4-yl]oxyphenyl]urea.

2-methylbutan-2-amine and phenyl n'-[3,5-bis(trifluoromethyl)phenyl]-n-cyanocarbamimidate react together in the presence of acetonitrile, n,n-diethylethanamine to produce 1-[3,5-bis(trifluoromethyl)phenyl]-3-cyano-2-(2-methylbutan-2-yl)guanidine.
(2-methylnaphthalen-1-yl)boronic acid and 1-bromo-2-methylnaphthalene react together in the presence of boronic acid, hydrogen peroxide to produce 2-methylnaphthalen-1-ol.
Ethyl 3,7-dimethyl-1h-indole-2-carboxylate reacts in the presence of oxolane, aluminum(3+), hydride, lithium(1+) to produce (3,7-dimethyl-1h-indol-2-yl)methanol.
Methyl 1h-indole-5-carboxylate reacts in the presence of acetic acid, oxidane, cyanoboranuide, sodium(1+), hydroxide to produce methyl 2,3-dihydro-1h-indole-5-carboxylate.

[(2s,4r)-4-[(4-methoxyphenyl)methylsulfanyl]-1-methylsulfonylpyrrolidin-2-yl]methyl methanesulfonate and phenylmethanamine react together in the presence of iodide, sodium(1+) to produce n-benzyl-1-[(2s,4r)-4-[(4-methoxyphenyl)methylsulfanyl]-1-methylsulfonylpyrrolidin-2-yl]methanamine.

Ethyl 3-aminopropanoate and 4-[[cyclohexyl-(3-methylthieno[3,2-b]pyridin-2-yl)methyl]amino]benzoic acid react together in the presence of n,n-diethylethanamine, 3-(ethyliminomethylideneamino)-n,n-dimethylpropan-1-amine, n,n-dimethylformamide, chlorane, oxidane, 1-hydroxybenzotriazole, chloride, azanium to produce ethyl 3-[[4-[[cyclohexyl-(3-methylthieno[3,2-b]pyridin-2-yl)methyl]amino]benzoyl]amino]propanoate.

2-[4-[(4-chlorophenyl)-phenylmethyl]piperazin-1-yl]ethanamine and 5-(4-cyclohexylphenyl)-1-phenylpyrazole-3-carbaldehyde react together to produce 2-[4-[(4-chlorophenyl)-phenylmethyl]piperazin-1-yl]-n-[[5-(4-cyclohexylphenyl)-1-phenylpyrazol-3-yl]methyl]ethanamine.

N-methylhydroxylamine and 3-(3,4-dimethoxyphenyl)prop-2-enoic acid react together in the presence of 2,2-dimethylpropanoyl chloride, n,n-diethylethanamine, ethyl acetate, ethoxyethane, n,n-dimethylformamide, chlorane to produce 3-(3,4-dimethoxyphenyl)-n-hydroxy-n-methylprop-2-enamide.

8-chloro-7-[(4-chlorophenyl)methyl]-3-ethyl-1-(3-hydroxypropyl)purine-2,6-dione reacts in the presence of propan-1-ol, sodium to produce 7-[(4-chlorophenyl)methyl]-3-ethyl-1-(3-hydroxypropyl)-8-propoxypurine-2,6-dione.

3-[4-(3-aminopropyl)phenyl]-1h-pyridazin-6-one and 2-chloroethanesulfonyl chloride react together in the presence of bromane, oxolane, n,n-diethylethanamine, 1,3-dimethylimidazolidin-2-one to produce n-[3-[4-(6-oxo-1h-pyridazin-3-yl)phenyl]propyl]ethenesulfonamide.
